  "title": "Introduction to Symptoms of Fever and Cold Sensations",
  "lessonText": "Understanding the symptoms of fever and cold sensations is crucial for effective management.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Fever often presents with elevated body temperature.\n- Cold sensations may include chills and shivering.\n- Symptoms can vary in intensity and duration.\n- Recognizing these symptoms helps in timely intervention."
  }
}
